#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast.md:2
msgid "## 1 功能作用说明"
msgstr "## 1 Function Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast.md:4
msgid "将两个张量广播到共同兼容的形状，使它们可以进行逐元素操作。"
msgstr "Broadcast two tensors to a common compatible shape so that they can perform element-wise operations."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast.md:6
msgid "**语法：**"
msgstr "**Syntax:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast.md:8
msgid "- `triton.language.broadcast(input, other)` - 函数调用形式"
msgstr "- `triton.language.broadcast(input, other)` - function call form"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast.md:10
msgid "**功能：**"
msgstr "**Function:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast.md:12
msgid ""
"- 自动对齐不同秩张量得到目标形状\n"
"- 将大小为1的维度扩展到目标形状中对应维度的大小\n"
msgstr ""
"- Automatically align tensors of different ranks to obtain the target shape  \n"
"- Expand dimensions of size 1 to match the corresponding dimension size in the target shape\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast.md:14
msgid "## 2 参数规格"
msgstr "## 2 Parameter Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast.md:16
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast.md:18
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 必需 | 说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|------|\n"
"| input | tensor | 是 | 第一个输入张量，必须为RankedTensorType |\n"
"| other | tensor | 是 | 第二个输入张量，必须为RankedTensorType |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Required | Description |\n"
"|--------|------|------|------|\n"
"| input | tensor | Yes | The first input tensor, must be of type RankedTensorType |\n"
"| other | tensor | Yes | The second input tensor, must be of type RankedTensorType |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast.md:20
msgid "**返回值：**"
msgstr "**Return value:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/broadcast.md:22
msgid ""
"- **类型：** tensor\n"
"- **形状：** 两个tensor共同兼容的目标形状\n"
"- **数据类型：** 每个返回的张量保持其输入的原始数据类型\n"
"- **内存布局：**返回新创建的张量\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Type:** tensor  \n"
"- **Shape:** The target shape that two tensors are compatible with together  \n"
"- **Data Type:** Each returned tensor retains the original data type of its input  \n"
"- **Memory Layout:** Returns a newly created tensor\n"

